{
  "texts": [
    "The first one is as follows.",
    "You have two coins, one of value 1 unit, an another of value 2 units.",
    "For a given required total, you must minimize the difference in the number of coins used.",
    "So for a total of 100 units, use 34 1 unit coins and 33 2 unit coins.",
    "ChatGPT's solution was: def m i ni m i z e_ c o i n_ d i f fe r e n ce ( total): # calculate the number of 2 unit coins needed num_twos = total // 2 # calculate the remaining amount remainder = total % 2 # calculate the number of 1 unit coins needed for the remaining amount num_ones = remainder # calculate the difference in the number of coins used diff = abs ( num_twos -num_ones) # check if using the smaller denomination first results in a smaller difference if total % 2!"
  ]
}